    "body": "### Problem\n\nThe `menu` field of completion items is sometimes way too long:\r\n\r\n![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/548a46c5-2a40-4270-97a5-ae4eea3526d8)\r\n\r\nIt would be great to have a way to hide this field if you don't need it\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nYou should be able to hide specific completion item fields using `'completepopup'` or some other option",
